Description: PG 19+ moved get_database_name declaration from commands/dbcommands.h
to utils/lsyscache.h. zhparser.c calls get_database_name() (line ~216) so under
PG 19 the declaration is missing -> implicit-function-declaration error with the
Xcode 26.5 toolchain.
Upstream: equivalent to PR #96 (bigplaice) merged to master after the v2.3 tag,
so this is not in any released tarball yet.

--- a/zhparser.c
+++ b/zhparser.c
@@ -17,6 +17,10 @@
 #include "utils/varlena.h"
 #endif
 
+#if PG_VERSION_NUM >= 190000
+#include "utils/lsyscache.h"
+#else
 #include "commands/dbcommands.h"
+#endif
 
 /* dict file extension */
